sequenceDiagram
    participant KFTO as Kubeflow Training Operator
    participant AccLaunch as accelerate_launch.py<br/>Container Entry Point
    participant SFT as sft_trainer.py<br/>Training Orchestration
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant PVCIn as PVC /data/input<br/>Filesystem
    participant GPU as NVIDIA GPU<br/>CUDA 12.1
    participant FSDP as FSDP Workers<br/>29500/TCP plaintext
    participant PVCOut as PVC /data/output<br/>Filesystem
    participant Tracker as MLflow/Aim/ClearML<br/>HTTP/HTTPS configurable

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over KFTO, PVCOut: Flow 1: Training Job Execution
        KFTO->>AccLaunch: Launch PyTorchJob Pod<br/>Kubernetes API (TLS 1.2+)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
        AccLaunch->>AccLaunch: Parse JSON config<br/>(SFT_TRAINER_CONFIG_JSON_PATH)
        AccLaunch->>AccLaunch: Auto-detect GPU count<br/>(torch.cuda.device_count)
        AccLaunch->>AccLaunch: Apply FSDP defaults
        AccLaunch->>SFT: Launch training (in-process)
        SFT->>HFHub: Download model & tokenizer<br/>GET /api/models/{model_id}<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (HF_TOKEN)
        HFHub-->>SFT: Model weights & config
        SFT->>PVCIn: Load training dataset<br/>Filesystem (POSIX permissions)
        PVCIn-->>SFT: JSON/JSONL/Arrow/Parquet data
        SFT->>SFT: Tokenize & preprocess data<br/>(DataPreProcessor handler chain)
        SFT->>GPU: Initialize model on GPU<br/>PCIe/NVLink
        loop Training Loop (per epoch)
            SFT->>GPU: Forward pass
            GPU-->>SFT: Loss tensor
            SFT->>FSDP: Synchronize gradients<br/>29500/TCP c10d static rendezvous<br/>plaintext (no encryption)
            FSDP-->>SFT: Aggregated gradients
            SFT->>GPU: Backward pass & optimizer step
            opt Trainer Controller Rules
                SFT->>SFT: Evaluate rules (simpleeval)<br/>e.g. loss > threshold
            end
            opt Experiment Tracking
                SFT->>Tracker: Log metrics (loss, lr, epoch)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Auth: URI/API key
            end
        end
        SFT->>PVCOut: Save model checkpoint<br/>Filesystem (POSIX permissions)
        PVCOut-->>SFT: Write confirmation
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over AccLaunch, PVCOut: Flow 2: vLLM Adapter Post-Processing
        AccLaunch->>PVCOut: Read checkpoint directory<br/>(adapter_model.safetensors)
        AccLaunch->>AccLaunch: post_process_vLLM_adapters<br/>Extract new embeddings
        AccLaunch->>PVCOut: Write new_embeddings.safetensors
        AccLaunch->>PVCOut: Write .complete sentinel file
    end
